review_blob:
Hands down, best beer Ive ever had.
The taste is quite sweet, yet a bit bitter. (it gets sweeter and more bitter as it gets warmer)
Tastes like rye bread, caramel and a bit like chocolate.

Bought in a 0.5l bottle.
A sweetened beer, that tasted a lot like rye bread and caramel.
For beer thats sold on shelf, its near perfect!

A pleasant surprise from Cesu Brewery.
Probably the best beer Ive tasted in the price-range.
Certainly better than most beers available on shelf.
